Package: aire.zmvm
Type: Package
Title: Download pollution data for the Zona Metropolitana del Valle de Mexico
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:  c(person("Diego", "Valle-Jones", email = "diego@diegovalle.net", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: The Mexico City government mantains a network of censors to continually monitor
    pollution. This package provides R functions that can download the daily maximum, minimum,
    hourly average or real-time data for each of the pollution measuring stations or geographic
    zones. It also contains the locations of each of the stations. See <http://www.aire.df.gob.mx/>
    for the air pollution website.
License: BSD_3_clause + file LICENSE
